title: Champs you won't buy?
body:
I own every champ except Yorick, Tahm and Zac.
I have about 33k IP and every time I go to the store to complete my collection I just stare at them for a few minutes before going to do something else.
Absolutely no interest in owning these 3.
{{champion:223}} {{champion:83}} {{champion:154}} 

How bout you, GD?
